summary: My character preset for you to enjoy
descriptionHtml:
Racemenu preset for my Nord character Skyla. Ive included a screenshot of what she looks like without vampirism.

Mods used:

[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/29624/?]Racemenu[/url]
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/68311/?]KS Hairdos Renewal[/url]
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/22701/?]Seductive Lips HD[/url]
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/35267/?]SG Female Textures Renewal[/url]
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/13722/?]The Eyes of Beauty-PLAYER[/url]
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/31665/?]Better Makeup fo SKSE[/url]

I don't use a ENB or anything so as long as you use the mods listed above you will get the same result.
Full credit goes to the author's of the mods used, without your amazing work Skyrim would be dull and boring.
Share your screenshots and enjoy :)
